{"tid":626874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★窩蛋雙皮奶炸傷女客","createTime":"2018-04-12T13:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T07:47:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c08c6c01bc56f9802d079d8e0bc8fe960a3172","tid":626874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:04:54.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合報道】窩蛋雙皮奶是受歡迎的甜品，但卻發生「炸蛋」意外！<span style=\"color: red;\">廣東韶關</span>一名龍姓女子近日與友人到當地餐廳食用「窩蛋雙皮奶」，奶中的窩蛋竟突然炸開，高溫的雙皮奶飛濺而出，把她的頸部、手臂以及臉部灼傷，令她幾乎破相。餐廳負責人承認製作雙皮奶時程序失當，但未提及是否會向龍女作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180412/photo/0412-00178-023b1.jpg?t=1523538279680\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180412%2Fphoto%2F0412-00178-023b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1523538279680&h=829b835f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180412/00178_023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180412%2F00178_023.html&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f6ed724f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180412/00178_023.html</a>"},{"pid":"c4fba4c8b0507982e699b449a1baa5428c5fb31c","tid":626874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31616fc8c9ddb4a307bced5c6e3280d5c99513c","tid":626874,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img3.qianzhan123.com/star/e5/e5576d9f/e5576d9f.large.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.qianzhan123.com%2Fstar%2Fe5%2Fe5576d9f%2Fe5